10. Risks & Mitigations

Risk	Likelihood	Impact	Mitigation
Google Play scraper blocked or rate-limited	Medium	High	Use delays between requests; cache scraped data locally; use Kaggle dataset as fallback
BERT training too slow on local machine	High	Medium	Use Google Colab (free GPU); alternatively use distilBERT for faster inference
Aspect keyword lists miss edge cases	Medium	Medium	Expand keyword lists iteratively using frequent unmatched terms from exploratory analysis
React dashboard integration complexity	Low	Medium	Start with static mock data in frontend before connecting to live API
Data quality issues (very short reviews)	High	Low	Apply minimum token length filter (>= 5 tokens) during preprocessing

